Program: Outlook
Title: Rape Victim Presses Charges
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsdb
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The rape victim seeking justice 20 years later after her attacker calls to apologise. Also, what its like using the Mumbai train system after the recent bombs. The Phelophepa Healthcare Train set up by Lynette Coetzee and Lillian Cingo. G Cel, the Los Angeles gangster turning to rap music. Finally the Hindu family given permission to hold a traditional funeral byre ceremony in the UK. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less